title: Marbella Sessions 2014 [Pool Party Mix, VIP Club Mix] (2CD) (Aci
description:
Marbella Sessions 2014 [Pool Party Mix, VIP Club Mix] 

                    Club, Funky, House | Ministry Of Sound

           VBR kbps | MP3 | Mixed + Split | 2014 | 02:33:09 | 513 Mb


We kick off this year's exclusive album with the Pool Party Mix leading with our very own future hit 'I Wanna Feel' from Second City alongside #1 singles from Duke Dumont, Route 94, Sam Smith and Naughty Boy before we move into chart topping smashes from Gorgon City, Klangkarussell and Lana Del Ray. As we continue onto the second mix we bring you the perfect soundtrack to your night out with the VIP Club Mix featuring huge main room hits from the biggest names in dance music including Avicii, Calvin Harris, Martin Garrix, DVBBS & Borgeous and Rudimental, of course no party mix would be complete without a couple of classic tracks, so for good measure we've chucked in anthems from Lonyo, Indo and The Swedish House Mafia.
